= etch
Al Idian <al.idian@acm.org>
:description: View PDF metadata

`etch` uses `exiftool` to view PDF metadata.
Please note this software is provided "as is", without warranty of any kind.

Usage:

1. Clone this repo.
2. (Optional) Set permissions and view the help text.

+
[source,bash]
----
chmod 700 ./etch
./etch --help
----

3. Run `etch`.

+
[source,bash]
----
./etch /your-file.pdf
----
